description: This file appears to be a C source file implementing various API functions for cellular management, including parameter getters/setters, interface management, network information retrieval, and related cellular operations within a module likely associated with RDK (Reference Design Kit) or similar firmware.

classes.name: PCELLULARMGR_CELLULAR_DATA

classes.name: PCELLULAR_INTERFACE_CONTEXTPROFILE_INFO
